    "Due to the limited experimentally verified circRNA-miRNA interactions, the classic algorithm miRanda was used to predict potential relationships with circRNA and miRNA.",
    "The data of circRNA and miRNA were extracted from circBase and miRBase databases, respectively.",
    "Associations between miRNAs and diseases, which were experimentally validated, were then collected from the HMDD3.2 database [43].",
    "We collected 17,844 circRNA-miRNA associations (585 circRNAs and 640 miRNAs) and 1883 disease-miRNA associations (88 diseases and 462 genes).",
    "Human circRNA-gene-disease associationsModern medicine has proved that human diseases are directly or indirectly related to genes."
